---
import Heading from './Heading.astro';
import Text from './Text.astro';

// Component: Catalyst (Module 03)
// Physics: Full-Screen | Snap-Point
---
<section 
  id="catalyst" 
  class="h-screen w-full snap-start flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center p-8 section-module narrative-locked" 
  data-index="2" 
  data-auto-scroll="true"
  data-auto-scroll-ms="9000"
  data-animation-delay="2500"
>
  <Heading 
    as="h2" 
    visualRank="vr1" 
    class="mb-8 max-w-4xl opacity-0 translate-y-4 staccato-text"
    data-delay="0"
    data-delay-absolute="true"
  >
    Connection is a process, not meaningless interactions.
  </Heading>
  
  <Text 
    visualRank="vr2" 
    class="max-w-xl opacity-0 translate-y-4 staccato-text"
    data-delay="4000"
    data-delay-absolute="true"
  >
    From isolation to connection, the journey starts within.
  </Text>
</section>
